<action name=FORTUNE(1)>FORTUNE(1)</action>                                             <action name=FORTUNE(1)>FORTUNE(1)</action>

NAME
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            fortune - sample lines from a file

SYNOPSIS
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            fortune \[ file \]

DESCRIPTION
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            Fortune prints a one-line aphorism chosen at random. If a
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            file is specified, the saying is taken from that file\;
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            otherwise it is selected from /lib/games/fortunes.

FILES
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            /lib/games/fortunes
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            /lib/games/fortunes.index   fast lookup table, maintained
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            automatically

SOURCE
<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>            /appl/cmd/fortune.b

<style color=#00ffffff size=1>.</style>                                Inferno Manual
